subject: Football (College)
Bowl Games
lead_paragraph: Melvin Gordon had 251 yards and three touchdowns, and Rafael Gaglianone kicked a 25-yard field goal in overtime, as No. 17 Wisconsin beat No. 19 Auburn on Thursday.
